<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#Player">
  <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A person who plays games.</rdfs:comment>
  <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Player</rdfs:label>
  <vaem:rationale>[Ontology Generation Agent] Created class Player: Required by CQ01, CQ02, CQ03, CQ05, CQ07, CQ22, CQ24, CQ25, CQ26, CQ27, CQ29, CQ35, CQ52, CQ55, CQ56, CQ57, CQ64, CQ65, CQ66
    [Logical Consistency Agent] Created class Player: Required by CQ01, CQ02, CQ03, CQ05, CQ07, CQ22, CQ24, CQ25, CQ26, CQ27, CQ35, CQ52, CQ55, CQ56, CQ57, CQ64, CQ65, CQ66
    [Pitfall Resolution Agent] Created class Player: Required by CQ01, CQ02, CQ03, CQ05, CQ07, CQ22, CQ24, CQ25, CQ26, CQ27, CQ29, CQ35, CQ52, CQ55, CQ56, CQ57, CQ64, CQ65, CQ66: Initial creation based on competency questions
    [Pitfall Resolution Agent] Created class Player: Required by CQ01, CQ02, CQ03, CQ05, CQ07, CQ22, CQ24, CQ25, CQ26, CQ27, CQ35, CQ52, CQ55, CQ56, CQ57, CQ64, CQ65, CQ66: Consistency check</vaem:rationale>
  <dc:source>(competency_question) CQ01: What is the username of the player?
    (competency_question) CQ02: Who are the friends of the player?
    (competency_question) CQ03: Who are the friends that play other games as well with this player?
    (competency_question) CQ05: What are the achievements of my friends?
    (competency_question) CQ07: What are the achievements your friend has received?
    (competency_question) CQ22: Who has the best kill count in the game?
    (competency_question) CQ24: What achievements has a player obtained?
    (competency_question) CQ25: What games has the player played?
    (competency_question) CQ26: What items does the player have?
    (competency_question) CQ27: What achievements of a certain type does the player have?
    (competency_question) CQ29: What is the last game a player has played?
    (competency_question) CQ35: In how many games does the player have all the achievements?
    (competency_question) CQ52: What equipment does a player have in a game?
    (competency_question) CQ55: What are the games where a player can use this item?
    (competency_question) CQ56: How many players have made in app purchases?
    (competency_question) CQ57: How many players who have already spent money, spend money again?
    (competency_question) CQ64: How long does a player spend in the game before making first IAP?
    (competency_question) CQ65: Where do the players live who have not made any IAP?
    (competency_question) CQ66: Where do the players who have done the most IAP live?</dc:source>
  <owl:disjointWith rdf:resource='http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#Game'/>
<owl:disjointWith rdf:resource='http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#Achievement'/>
<owl:disjointWith rdf:resource='http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#Item'/>
<owl:disjointWith rdf:resource='http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#Genre'/>
<owl:disjointWith rdf:resource='http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#AchievementType'/>
<owl:disjointWith rdf:resource='http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#InAppPurchase'/>
<owl:disjointWith rdf:resource='http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#Location'/>
<owl:disjointWith rdf:resource='http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#PlayingArea'/>
</owl:Class>

